    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The engine runs smoothly, and all major mechanical systems are in solid working order. While the exterior paint still shines, you will find some minor stone chips and light surface scratches upon close inspection. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing only light wear on the driver's seat bolster. It\u2019s a reliable, attractive car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
