    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. It offers a smooth and reliable driving experience, with a strong engine and a transmission that shifts seamlessly. The exterior is clean with only minor cosmetic blemishes, and the interior has been kept tidy, showing minimal signs of wear. All major systems are fully functional, making this a dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned car that is ready for the road.",
