    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2017 Lexus RX 350 in Nebula Gray Pearl. This vehicle strikes the perfect balance for a buyer seeking luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a deep shine, though I want to be transparent about a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scratch near the trunk handle. Inside, the Parchment leather cabin is smoke-free and inviting; the seats show only light natural creasing, and the genuine wood trim remains crack-free. Every feature, from the heated/ventilated seats to the power liftgate and navigation system, is in full working order. Under the hood, the V6 engine runs flawlessly. I have kept a detailed folder of all service records, including a recent transmission fluid flush and a fresh set of Michelin tires installed last year. It delivers a quiet, composed ride with no warning lights on the dash. This is a solid, honest car that has many miles of comfortable service left to give.",
      "price": 34800.0,
